\ HORN\ composer: Larry Polansky\ 2/3/90\\ 10/16/92  RDG  begin port to Mac/AudioMedia\ Tuning file, sets up SHAPES with tunings for the DSPANEW TASK-DSP_TUNINGSFPINIT\ SHAPES which contain harmonic series ob.shape DSP-1-SERIESob.shape DSP-5-SERIESob.shape DSP-3-SERIES: ALLOC.DSP.TUNINGS ( Ñ )	17 1 new: dsp-1-series ( freq )		1 put.data: dsp-1-series	17 1 new: dsp-5-series		5 put.data: dsp-5-series	17 1 new: dsp-3-series		3 put.data: dsp-3-series;: FREE.DSP.TUNINGS ( Ñ )	free: dsp-1-series 	free: dsp-5-series	free: dsp-3-series;: RATIO->FREQ ( num den fund -- fHz )	float swap float float  	( -- ) ( fund num den -- ) 	F/ F* 	F>I				( -- fHz );: STUFF.SERIES { fund series -- }	17  series  set.many: []	17 0  DO		i 1+ 1 fund  ratio->freq 		i series  put: []	LOOP	" Freq " 0  series put.dim.name: [];: FILL.DSP.TUNINGS  { | fund -- }	fundamental-hz @ -> fund	fund dsp-1-series  stuff.series	5 4 fund ratio->freq    ( -- 5/4 of fund )	dsp-3-series  stuff.series	3 2 fund ratio->freq    ( -- 3/2 of fund )	dsp-5-series  stuff.series;: INIT.DSP.TUNINGS  ( -- )	." Initializing DSP tunings " cr	alloc.dsp.tunings	fill.dsp.tunings;: TERM.DSP.TUNINGS  ( -- )	free.dsp.tunings;if.forgotten term.dsp.tunings